{"GYL542bYMps":{"id":"GYL542bYMps","type":"work","title":"慧山記","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《慧山記》•三卷","summary":"一名《九龍山志》。明邵寶撰。寶有《左觿》，已著錄。慧山即惠山，在無錫縣界，局狹而氣秀，地近而景幽，自昔號為佳境。寶居近是山，釣遊所及，時有品題。所作如《惠山雜歌》、《惠山十二詠》、《敘竹茶壚》等篇，具載於《容春堂續集》中。此書仿賀知章會稽洞、郭子美羅浮山之例，搜輯舊事遺文，為之作志。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=254633","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2712366","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052142","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v5","total_page":184,"paragraph_count":1574,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-qingtongzhikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NLG312001072075","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"清同治7年[1868]刻本","version":"v3","total_page":508,"paragraph_count":5038,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542PQLTR":{"id":"GYL542PQLTR","type":"work","title":"武夷山志","authors":[{"name":"裘仲孺","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《武夷山志》•十九卷","author_info":"明裘仲孺撰","summary":"明裘仲孺撰。仲孺字穉生，崇安人。洪武初，薦授平遠縣知縣。其書凡十一篇，首《名勝》，次《雲構》，次《題刻》，次《仙真》，次《羽流》，次《存疑》，次《物產》，次《遊寓》，次《祀典》，次《掞藻》，次《餘韻》。末一卷為《詞訂》，則詩文之續得者也。體例龐雜，殊不足觀。《掞藻》一篇，幾及全書之半，尤乖裁制也。","edition":"江蘇巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":19}},"GYL542pZSPq":{"id":"GYL542pZSPq","type":"work","title":"仙岩志","authors":[{"name":"王應辰","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《仙岩志》•六卷","author_info":"明王應辰撰","summary":"明王應辰撰，應辰自署曰舉人，不著裏貫。考《太學題名碑》有隆慶辛未進士王應辰，信陽人。去作此書時僅十六年，未知即其人否也。仙岩山在浙江里安縣境，為道書第二十六福地。嘉靖壬戌，兵部郎中永嘉王叔果屬應辰為此編。首載圖景，次錄詩文，序次尚頗簡潔。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":6}},"GYL5427ZLt7":{"id":"GYL5427ZLt7","type":"work","title":"江防總論","authors":[{"name":"姜宸英","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《江防總論》•一卷、《海防總論》•一卷","author_info":"國朝姜宸英撰","summary":"國朝姜宸英撰。宸英字西溟，慈谿人。康熙丁丑進士，官翰林院編修。己卯充順天鄉試副考官，為正考官修撰李蟠所累，逮問。蟠遣戍，宸英卒於獄。是二書載曹溶《學海類編》中。各冠《總論》於前，而條系其形勢之略於後，題曰《附錄》。案《江防論》末稱：“依海道所經，自廣東西路始，福建、浙江、江南、登萊、天津衛、遼陽，以次及之。”又括海南所經各省郡縣，自為一卷，與論後所附錄全不相應。又稱“其沿海山河，寇《舟宗》入犯分合，日本輿地，皆有圖”。今亦無圖。知曹溶刪節其文，非宸英之原帙也。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"related_works":[{"id":"GYLt1DZaACP","title":"海防總論"}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=811057","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-xuehaileibian","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CXHLB177","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"學海類編","version":"v3","total_page":11,"paragraph_count":7,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542nLTUK":{"id":"GYL542nLTUK","type":"work","title":"牛首山志","authors":[{"name":"盛時泰","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《牛首山志》•二卷","author_info":"明盛時泰撰","summary":"明盛時泰撰。時泰字仲交，江寧人。嘉靖中貢生。牛首山在江甯城南，一名天闕。是書首志《山名》，次志《岩洞》、《池泉》、《殿廬》、《草樹》、《法寶》、《遊覽》、《麗藻》。其文頗近遊記，不盡沿志書窠臼。其藝文多著出某書，亦明人所難。惟“地畝弓口”一條，全錄稟帖批詞，首尾不加刪削，殊失體例。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2}},"GYL5429jdxB":{"id":"GYL5429jdxB","type":"work","title":"秦邊紀略","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《秦邊紀略》•四卷","author_info":"不著撰人名氏","summary":"不著撰人名氏。書中首卷“河州條”注，內有“西夷部落三十有奇，康熙十四年圍衛城一月，康熙二十二年又犯衛地”之語。又四卷《近疆西夷傳》內載，康熙二十四年，祝囊同科爾坤十八部由古北口入覲事，則此書為康熙間人所作。首載河州及西寧、莊浪、涼州、甘州、肅州、靖遠、寧夏、延綏等衛形勢要害；次載西寧等衛南北邊堡；次載西寧等衛近疆及河套；次載外疆、近疆西夷傳，河套部落蒙古四十八部落考略，西域土地人物略。其論邊鄙疆域，及防守攻剿情形，一一詳悉。蓋國家初定西陲，中間遘王輔臣之叛，與滇、黔相煽。方用兵於內地，故近邊諸部，往往窺竊。後乃以次削平，馴為臣僕。此書所述，皆是時之形勢。方今聖武遠揚，天山南北二萬餘裏，皆置郡開屯，歸我疆宇。昔之所謂險要者，今皆在戶闥之間；昔之所謂強梁者，今皆隸賦役之籍。此書所述，皆無所用之。然在當時，則可謂留心邊政者矣。至北邊四十八部源委弗詳，且非秦地。其西域道裏以驛程考之，亦皆在茫昧之間。蓋一時得之傳聞，附錄卷末，均不足為典要。存而不論可矣。","comment":"──右“地理類”邊防之屬，二十一部、八十三卷，皆附《存目》。","edition":"直隸總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=407728","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=919326","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=7385880","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-tongzhianhuifanshuji","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NLG312001066784","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"同治11年安徽藩署敬義齋刻本","version":"v1","total_page":328,"paragraph_count":227,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-qianlongchaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052108","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"乾隆鈔本","version":"v1","total_page":413,"paragraph_count":3698,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542XH9Pd":{"id":"GYL542XH9Pd","type":"work","title":"雁山志","authors":[{"name":"朱諫","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《雁山志》•四卷","author_info":"明朱諫撰","summary":"明朱諫撰。諫號蕩南，樂清人。弘治丙辰進士，官至吉安府知府。雁蕩山在溫州府，跨樂清、平陽二縣，於古無稱，自宋太平興國中，始有僧居之，奇秀甲於浙東。明初僧永昇者，始輯為《雁山集》一卷，編次無法。嘉靖己亥，諫因舊本搜討，增為四卷，列三十二門，樂清知縣徽州潘潢序之。萬曆辛巳，知州南昌胡汝寧複為翻雕，而以續得詩文冠於卷前，殊為猥雜。","edition":"浙江汪啟淑家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=818269","type":"text","details":"實行、廖壽彭"},{"id":"shidianguji-qianlongshijiuxukand","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY0398","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"乾隆十九年序刊道光二十八年重印本","version":"v4","total_page":233,"paragraph_count":163,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542tsLgX":{"id":"GYL542tsLgX","type":"work","title":"武夷山志略","authors":[{"name":"徐表然","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《武夷山志略》•四卷","author_info":"明徐表然撰","summary":"明徐表然撰。表然字德望，崇安人。嘉靖中嘗結漱藝山房於武夷第三曲，因撰次是書，分為四集。繪山之全圖，及武夷宮左各景，宮右九曲諸勝，悉以題詠附於後。凡名勝、古跡，皆分附於《山川》。較他地志尤便省覽，此變例之可取者。至於《寓賢》及《仙真》之類，人繪一圖，則不免近兒戲矣。其名《志略》者，謂茲山已有全志也。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4}},"GYL542UTEPH":{"id":"GYL542UTEPH","type":"work","title":"金山雜誌","authors":[{"name":"楊循吉","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《金山雜誌》•一卷","author_info":"明楊循吉撰","summary":"明楊循吉撰。循吉有《蘇州府纂修識略》，已著錄。金山在吳縣西三十裏，循吉少時，嘗讀書其中。歸田後因為之志。分八篇，一《山勢》，二《品石》，三《泉》，四《山居》，五《遊觀》，六《草木》，七《飲食》，八《勝事》，每篇各有論贊。","edition":"浙江汪汝瑮家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY5942","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":10,"paragraph_count":7,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542w3dkb":{"id":"GYL542w3dkb","type":"work","title":"阿育王山志","authors":[{"name":"郭子章","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《阿育王山志》•十卷","author_info":"明郭子章撰","summary":"明郭子章撰。子章有《蠙衣生易解》，已著錄。阿育王山在浙江寧波府，去府治四十裏。山有阿育王寺舍利塔，相傳為地中湧出，因以名寺，遂因以名山。蓋緇流梵笈有是異聞，年祀綿遠，亦無從而究詰也。是志凡分十類。揆其大旨，主於闡釋氏之顯應。故標茲靈跡，以啟彼信心，原不以核訂地理、考證古今為事也。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10}},"GYL542kAAQF":{"id":"GYL542kAAQF","type":"work","title":"仙都山志","authors":[{"name":"戴葵","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《仙都山志》•二卷","author_info":"明戴葵撰","summary":"明戴葵撰。葵，酆都人。始末未詳。據其自跋，此書蓋嘉靖丁未作也。仙都山在四川酆都縣境，為道經第四十二福地，稱前漢王方平、後漢陰長生得道處。葵雜采舊文，分為八類，大抵神仙家言為多。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2}},"GYL542LXjbd":{"id":"GYL542LXjbd","type":"work","title":"天臺山志","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《天臺山志》•一卷","author_info":"不著撰人名氏","summary":"不著撰人名氏。末稱世祖皇帝封道士王中立為仁靖純素真人，知為元人所作。又稱前至元間，知為順帝時人矣。其書頗典雅可觀，惟“七十二福地”一條，不引杜光庭書而引《記纂淵海》，知為稗販之學矣。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/天台山志","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=79305","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-shanghaihanfenlouyin","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/DZ0603","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"上海涵芬樓影印明《正統道藏》本","version":"v4","total_page":42,"paragraph_count":53,"check_type":"精校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542ftwy1":{"id":"GYL542ftwy1","type":"work","title":"衡嶽志","authors":[{"name":"彭簪","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《衡嶽志》•十三卷","author_info":"明彭簪撰","summary":"明彭簪撰，姚宏謨重訂。考《明史•藝文志》，載彭簪《衡嶽志》八卷。此多五卷，當即宏謨所增。然宏謨序已稱“續刻者隨時竄入而不之究”，則未經重修以前已非簪之原本矣。序又稱“總《形勝》於多景之前，補《事紀》於諸卷之首”，此本一卷為《事紀》，二卷、三卷為《形勢》，知為宏謨所增。至所稱“詩文以景附，景以類分”者，則散綴各卷，不可複考。簪自號石屋山人，安城人。官衡山縣知縣。其書成於嘉靖戊子。宏謨，秀水人。嘉靖癸丑進士，官至吏部左侍郎。其書成於隆慶辛未。時提督湖廣學政，應知縣章宣之請，續此編雲。","edition":"浙江汪啟淑家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":13},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5594088","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052144","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":252,"paragraph_count":2063,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542SKdAf":{"id":"GYL542SKdAf","type":"work","title":"震澤編","authors":[{"name":"蔡昇","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《震澤編》•八卷","author_info":"明蔡昇撰","summary":"明蔡昇撰。王鏊重修。昇字景東，吳江人。鏊有《史餘》，已著錄。是書首紀五湖七十二山兩洞庭，次石泉古跡，次風俗人物、土產、賦稅，次水利、官署、寺觀、菴廟、雜記，次集詩、集文。前有弘治十八年楊循吉序，稱其“操觚之妙，天機獨運。中間有似《爾雅》者，有似《山海經》者，有似柳子厚諸山水記者，用能繪畫造物，陳諸簡牘”。未免譽過其實。昇書本名《太湖志》，鏊為重修，乃取《禹貢》之語改今名雲。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4531110","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052131","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":438,"paragraph_count":3195,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NLG312001075714","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v2","total_page":373,"paragraph_count":982,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-mingwanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ8920939208314","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明萬曆刻本","version":"v2","total_page":373,"paragraph_count":910,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542y8Z7m":{"id":"GYL542y8Z7m","type":"work","title":"雲門志略","authors":[{"name":"張元忭","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《雲門志略》•五卷","author_info":"明張元忭撰","summary":"明張元忭撰。元忭有《紹興府志》，已著錄。雲門山在會稽城南。元至正十年，相裏允若作《雲門集》，黃溍序之。元忭以其未備，補緝是編。以《山川》、《古跡》、《名賢》為一卷，而餘四卷皆《藝文》，又末大於本矣。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":5},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5669451","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052176","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":302,"paragraph_count":1443,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL5421mTK5":{"id":"GYL5421mTK5","type":"work","title":"延綏鎮志","authors":[{"name":"譚吉璁","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《延綏鎮志》•六卷","author_info":"國朝譚吉璁撰","summary":"國朝譚吉璁撰。吉璁，字舟石，嘉興人。由內閣中書官至登州府知府。明時以延綏為重鎮，設重兵以防河套。本朝順治初年，罷延綏巡撫不設，而延綏鎮尚仍舊名。康熙十二年，吉璁以延安府同知分駐榆林城，乃因明巡撫塗宗濬舊本，重修此志。自《圖譜》至《藝文》，凡分十二類。所載皆明代邊防之事。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":6},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3677088","type":"text"}]},"GYL542JMSXZ":{"id":"GYL542JMSXZ","type":"work","title":"仙都志","authors":[{"name":"道士陳性定","role":"撰","dynasty":"元"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《仙都志》•二卷","author_info":"元道士陳性定撰","summary":"元道士陳性定撰。仙都山古名縉雲山，唐天寶中敕改今名。此志分六門，曰《山川》，曰《祠宇》，曰《神仙》，曰《高士》，曰《草木》，曰《碑碣題詠》。前序題至正戊子，不著姓名，以序及志中《祠宇門》考之，蓋元延祐中給道士趙嗣祺五品印，提點是山玉虛宮。羽流榮之，因撰是志也。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/仙都志","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=71103","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=284494","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=531200","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-qushitieqintongjianl","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02086584","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"瞿氏鐵琴銅劍樓抄本","version":"v4","total_page":72,"paragraph_count":94,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-shanghaihanfenlouyin","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/DZ0602","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"上海涵芬樓影印明《正統道藏》本","version":"v3","total_page":82,"paragraph_count":336,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052121","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"抄本","version":"v3","total_page":157,"paragraph_count":189,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542dietw":{"id":"GYL542dietw","type":"work","title":"鄧尉山志","authors":[{"name":"沈津","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《鄧尉山志》•一卷","author_info":"明沈津撰","summary":"明沈津撰。津字潤卿，蘇州人。是書分《本志》、《泉石》、《祠墓》、《梵宇》、《山居》、《名釋》、《草木》、《食品》、《集詩》、《集文》十類。前為《總敘》一篇。其稱《本志》者，以專紀山之形勢為作志本意，故以冠於各類之首也。書成於嘉靖壬寅，靳學顏嘗為之序。黃虞稷《千頃堂書目》遂以為學顏所作，失考甚矣。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL542rjjTu":{"id":"GYL542rjjTu","type":"work","title":"黃海","authors":[{"name":"潘之恒","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《黃海》•六十卷","author_info":"明潘之恒撰","summary":"明潘之恒撰。之恒字景昇，歙縣人。嘉靖間官中書舍人。考《明史•藝文志》有潘之恒《黃海》二十九卷，此本雖卷數未標，其曰《紀初》者八，曰《紀藏》者七，曰《紀跡》者十有八，曰《紀遊》者二十有一，曰《紀異》者六，皆別之為卷，則已六十卷矣。史稱二十九卷，未為確數。然其中次第卷數，或有或闕，或參差錯互，蓋猶未定之稿，不知其止此六十卷否也。黃山在徽州府西北百三十裏，舊名黟山，唐改今名。跨據宣、池、江、浙數郡。世傳黃帝與容成子、浮邱公煉藥於此，故有浮邱、容成諸峰。此姑存圖經之說，以備古跡一條則可。之恒竟上溯軒轅，采摭經傳，凡語涉黃帝者皆入焉。至以《廣黃帝本行紀》、《真仙通鑒》諸書與六經之文並列，何其誕歟！大抵以多為勝，而考證之學與著述之體則非所講也。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":60},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=1961400","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052159","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":1577,"paragraph_count":1635,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL5424e4As":{"id":"GYL5424e4As","type":"work","title":"蠻司合志","authors":[{"name":"毛奇齡","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蠻司合志》•十五卷","author_info":"國朝毛奇齡撰","summary":"國朝毛奇齡撰。奇齡有《仲氏易》，已著錄。是編皆紀明代土司始末。凡湖廣一卷，貴州二卷，四川四卷，雲南四卷，兩廣四卷。亦其修史所餘之稿也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":15},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=815676","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3090192","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-guangxuzhonghuijixus","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL01025929","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"光緒中會稽徐氏鑄學齋本","version":"v6","total_page":472,"paragraph_count":3444,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxikexihehejiben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02086897","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙刻西河合集本","version":"v2","total_page":470,"paragraph_count":4670,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxikexihehejiben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052101","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙刻西河合集本","version":"v2","total_page":469,"paragraph_count":4653,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542FS9pK":{"id":"GYL542FS9pK","type":"work","title":"茅山志","authors":[{"name":"道士劉大彬","role":"撰","dynasty":"元"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《茅山志》•十五卷","author_info":"元道士劉大彬撰","summary":"元道士劉大彬撰。大彬號玉虛子，錢塘人。延祐中襲封茅山四十五代宗師，洞觀微妙元應真人。是書分《誥副墨》、《三神紀》、《括神區》、《稽古跡》、《道山冊》、《上清品》、《仙曹署》、《采真遊》、《樓觀部》、《靈植檢》、《錄金石》、《金薤編》十二門，每門以三字為題，蓋仿陶弘景《真誥》例也。前有永樂癸卯胡儼序，稱“舊本為張雨所書，至為精潔。後毀於兵，姚廣孝複為刊版。及成化庚寅、嘉靖庚戌又重刻者再”。此本即嘉靖時刻。不但紙版惡劣，非張雨之舊，且為無識道流續入明事，敍述凡鄙，亦非劉大彬之舊矣。","edition":"浙江孫仰曾家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":15},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/茅山志","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=497389","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=956787","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4247088","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-shanghaihanfenlouyin","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/DZ0304","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"上海涵芬樓影印明《正統道藏》本","version":"v17","total_page":917,"paragraph_count":2560,"check_type":"精校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kebenpeimingkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02086557","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本配明刻本","version":"v4","total_page":550,"paragraph_count":6633,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542ZQkcF":{"id":"GYL542ZQkcF","type":"work","title":"京口三山志","authors":[{"name":"張萊","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《京口三山志》•十卷","author_info":"明張萊撰","summary":"明張萊撰。萊字廷心，丹徒人。弘治間舉人。北固、金、焦三山，皆古來勝境，而未有裒輯遺文舊事，合為一志者。兗州史宗道為鎮江推官，始屬萊考三山名跡沿革，及歷代詩文，匯成此編，頗能訂訛正謬。如金山之名，舊雲創於唐李錡。萊則謂梁天監四年即金山修水陸會，其名已始於六朝。考證頗為典核。然如《事物紀原》引宋大中祥符七年四月詔，封焦山大聖祠為明應公，本非僻書僻事，而《祠廟類》中乃失收之，則疏密亦不免互見。蓋萊所依據，多取諸郡縣圖經，未能博徵群籍，故每有漏略也。","edition":"江蘇巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3083934","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA03180","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本(序刊)","version":"v6","total_page":448,"paragraph_count":745,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052137","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":470,"paragraph_count":867,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542Cqg5D":{"id":"GYL542Cqg5D","type":"work","title":"龍虎山志","authors":[{"name":"元明善","role":"撰","dynasty":"元"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《龍虎山志》•三卷","author_info":"元元明善撰","summary":"元元明善撰，明張國祥續修。明善字複初，清河人。以浙東使者薦，為學正。擢太子文學，曆翰林學士，諡文敏，事蹟具《元史》本傳。國祥則嗣封真人也。是書乃皇慶三年明善官翰林學士時奉敕所修。然原本體例，不可複考，惟存延祐元年程钜夫序及吳全節進表。此本載山川、建置、人物、道侶並累朝制敕、藝文，頗為龐雜。殆已多所竄亂，非其舊矣。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3067095","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=8488233","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-qianlongwuqibitangta","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY2516","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"乾隆五年(1740)棲碧堂太上清宮刻本","version":"v14","total_page":865,"paragraph_count":951,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-qianlongkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/ZWDS0218","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"乾隆刻本","version":"v3","total_page":192,"paragraph_count":351,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL542hysLB":{"id":"GYL542hysLB","type":"work","title":"廬山紀事","authors":[{"name":"桑喬","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《廬山紀事》•十二卷","author_info":"明桑喬撰","summary":"明桑喬撰，國朝範礽補訂。喬字子木，江都人。嘉靖壬辰進士，官至監察禦史。以首劾嚴嵩，為所構陷，謫戍九江以卒。事蹟具《明史》本傳。此書即其在戍所時作，成於嘉靖辛酉。至國朝順治戊戌，巡按禦史許世昌屬南康推官會稽範礽重為補訂。以山陰、山陽別其條貫，屬南康者列於陽，屬九江者列於陰。又取喬後百餘年間事蹟題詠，綴補於後。礽序稱喬書質而辨，文而約，紀事皆題原采書名。礽所補悉仿其例雲。","edition":"浙江汪汝瑮家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4567740","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=887715","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA03218","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本(序刊)","version":"v9","total_page":602,"paragraph_count":628,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02052147","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":1283,"paragraph_count":8827,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true}}